## 三、响应格式

### 3.1 成功响应

```json
// 单个资源
{
  "id": "session-123",
  "title": "My Chat",
  "createdAt": "2024-01-15T10:30:00Z",
  "mode": "chat"
}

// 资源列表
{
  "items": [
    { "id": "1", "title": "Chat 1" },
    { "id": "2", "title": "Chat 2" }
  ],
  "total": 100,
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 20
}

// 聊天响应（非流式）
{
  "content": "I'm doing well, thank you!",
  "attachments": [],
  "groundingMetadata": {
    "searchEntryPoint": { ... },
    "groundingChunks": [ ... ]
  }
}
```

### 3.2 错误响应

```json
// 标准错误
{
  "code": "VALIDATION_ERROR",
  "message": "Invalid request parameters",
  "details": {
    "field": "email",
    "error": "Invalid email format"
  }
}

// 提供商错误
{
  "code": "API_KEY_ERROR",
  "message": "Invalid or expired API key",
  "recoverable": false,
  "context": {
    "providerId": "google",
    "operation": "chat",
    "requestId": "req-123"
  }
}
```

### 3.3 HTTP 状态码

| 状态码 | 含义 | 使用场景 |
|--------|------|----------|
| 200 | OK | 成功读取/更新 |
| 201 | Created | 成功创建资源 |
| 204 | No Content | 成功删除 |
| 400 | Bad Request | 请求参数错误 |
| 401 | Unauthorized | 未认证 |
| 403 | Forbidden | 无权限 |
| 404 | Not Found | 资源不存在 |
| 409 | Conflict | 资源冲突 |
| 422 | Unprocessable | 业务逻辑错误 |
| 429 | Too Many Requests | 速率限制 |
| 500 | Internal Error | 服务器错误 |

